# VPN_SWITCH_BINARY_wireguard - WireGuard process binary
#
# Used to identify running WireGuard processes and to execute WireGuard commands.
# This follows the VPN_SWITCH_BINARY_<protocol> naming convention for
# protocol-agnostic binary lookup.
#
# Default: wg-quick (from package: wireguard-tools)
# With privilege elevation: sudo wg-quick or doas wg-quick
#
# Used by:
#   - check_and_create_session(): Detect running VPN processes
#   - _wireguard_connect1(): Execute WireGuard connection
#   - _wireguard_disconnect1(): Execute WireGuard disconnection
